o-host\n|-\n|2015\n|''[[Celebrity Family Feud]]''\n|Episode: \"Lawrence vs Lopez\"\n|-\n|2016\n|''[[Cupcake Wars]]''\n|Runner Up\n|-\n|2017\u20132019\n|''[[Hawaii Five-0 (2010 TV series)|Hawaii Five-0]]''\n|Aaron Wright\n|4 episodes\n|-\n|2019\n|''[[Celebrity Big Brother 2 (U.S. season)|Celebrity Big Brother]]''\n|Himself / Houseguest<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/celebrity-big-brother-cast-revealed-ryan-lochte-anthony-scaramucci-dina-lohan-more-1175684|title='Celebrity Big Brother' Cast Includes Anthony Scaramucci, Dina Lohan and Ryan Lochte|last=Porreca|first=Brian|date=13 January 2019|website=www.hollywoodreporter.com/|publisher=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]|access-date=13 January 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://ew.com/tv/2019/01/13/celebrity-big-brother-cast-anthony-scaramucci/|title=Anthony Scaramucci among 12 new Celebrity Big Brother houseguests|last=Ross|first=Dalton|date=13 January 2019|website=www.ew.com/|publisher=[[Entertainment Weekly]]|access-date=13 January 2019}}</ref>\n|9th place\n|-\n|2019\n|''[[Dollface]]''\n|Himself\n|Episode: \"Mystery Brunette\"\n|}\n\n===Dancing with the Stars===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! rowspan=2|Week#\n! rowspan=2|Dance / Song\n! colspan=3|Judge's scores\n! rowspan=2|Result\n! rowspan=2|Ref\n|-\n!Inaba\n!Goodman\n!Tonioli\n|-\n|1\n|[[Cha-cha-cha (dance)|Cha-Cha-Cha]] / \"[[I Like the Way (BodyRockers song)|I Like the Way (You Move)]]\"\n|7\n|7\n|7\n|\n| rowspan=9|<ref>{{Citation|title=Dancing with the Stars (U.S. season 3)|date=2018-08-20|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Dancing_with_the_Stars_(U.S._season_3)&oldid=855806923|work=Wikipedia|language=en|access-date=2018-08-26}}</ref>\n|-\n|2\n|[[Quickstep]] / \"[[I Got Rhythm]]\"\n|10\n|9\n|10\n|\n|-\n|3\n|[[Jive (dance)|Jive]] / \"[[Blue Suede Shoes]]\"\n|8\n|6\n|8\n|\n|-\n|4\n|[[Waltz]] / \"[[Take It to the Limit (Eagles song)|Take It to the Limit]]\"\n|9\n|9\n|9\n|\n|-\n|5\n|[[Samba]] / \"[[Freedom! '90]]\"\n|8\n|8\n|9\n